title: 299. #75HARD vs Kyle "The Captain" Creek
itunes:title: 299. #75HARD vs Kyle "The Captain" Creek
description: In today's episode, Andy is joined in the studio by author & creative director Kyle Creek. They discuss why Kyle needed to do #75HARD at a desperate time in his life, how it has helped improve his professional & personal life as a father, and the power this program has to make America a stronger nation.
